 substrate as a function of hair diameter, 
\begin_inset Formula $D_{h}$
\end_inset

.
 Volume of each fluid bridge, 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{f}$
\end_inset

, scales relative to 
\begin_inset Formula $D_{h}$
\end_inset

 based on the parameter 
